==>STEP NUM: 21
==>ACT: southwest
==>OBSERVATION: Blacksmith
Here you see a heavy forge and a few scrap pieces of iron and steel lying on the floor.  An anvil sits in the middle of the room, and next to it is a small barrel that at one time held water and a large one that held oil.  The exit is to the northeast.

You can see a gear here.

