==>STEP NUM: 81
==>ACT: south
==>OBSERVATION: Town of Ember
This small town looks as if it isn't very old.  The buildings, though small and ramshackle, all have fresh paint on them and the parts that are falling off seem due to poor craftsmanship instead of time.  There are some shops to the west, a town square to the south, and a road leads north.
