==>STEP NUM: 82
==>ACT: west
==>OBSERVATION: Shops
These shops seem in somewhat better condition than the rest of the town, especially the carpenter's.  However, all of the doors are closed and signs reading "Closed due to wild Eranti" adorn almost all.  To the east is the town proper.
